rComments: The worst teacher i have ever had. it was her first time teaching and hopefully for all students sake, her last. i taught myself everything and only did well in the class because i had a great TA who should have taught the class, she had to correct the prof enough times! dont take her if you can help it!!!

although this is her first time teaching the class, i think she did really well, considering the difficulty of the class. she tried to imrpove on things that weren't working, and it turned out ok at the end. she has tons of office hours to get help, and very accessable. give her some time and she'll be fine.

This was her first real class, and she was pretty bad. She couldnt explain anything very well, and I had to teach myself everything. But the TA's were great, and the book was actually  pretty clear. The midterms were easy, and the homework is worth 50% of your grade. It doesnt take much to do well in the class, especially with all the extra credit.
Monica is great!! She gives out lots of extra credit to help boost your grade. If you do all of the homework assignments, you can absolutely pass the 2 midterms and the Final.
